PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 24 - which declares the flooding caused by heaving rains in November of 1996 in the province of Quebec (Montreal and Mauricie regions), to be of concern to the federal government, and authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
